  "prompt": "How many questions are asked on Quora each minute on average?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2021, Quora does not publicly disclose the exact number of questions asked per minute. However, data from previous years suggested that thousands of questions are asked daily. Some estimates suggested around 5,000 to 10,000 questions per day, which would average out to around 3 to 7 questions per minute. For the most accurate and up-to-date statistics, it would be best to refer to Quora's official statistics or updates directly from their platform.",
